{tutorial}
{subtitle}Teaching Others{.subtitle}

{text}Now that I know RML, I want to teach my friends! Here's what I tell them:{.text}

{info}RML is perfect for beginners because it uses simple English words instead of confusing abbreviations.{.info}

{example}
{bold}Instead of this HTML:{.bold}
{code}&lt;h1&gt;Title&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Text&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Bold&lt;/strong&gt;{.code}

{bold}We write this RML:{.bold}
{code}{title}Title{.title}
{text}Text{.text}
{bold}Bold{.bold}{.code}

{text}See how much clearer that is?{.text}
{.example}
{.tutorial}

