{quiz}
{bold}Quick Self-Test{.bold}

{question}1. How do you close an RML tag?{.question}
{answer}With a dot before the tag name: {code}{.tagname}{.code}{.answer}

{question}2. What's better about RML than HTML?{.question}
{answer}
- Uses plain English words
- Clear opening and closing syntax  
- No confusing angle brackets
- Built-in educational features
{.answer}

{question}3. How do you make text bold in RML?{.question}
{answer}Use {code}{bold}text{.bold}{.code} or the shortcut {code}**text**{.code}{.answer}
{.quiz}

